metadata.name: The Art of War: Kingdoms #1
metadata.description: AoW: Kingdoms features 1,555 1/1s split between three factions (Land, Sea, and Air) and two sides (Good and Evil). Each NFT is expertly crafted using mixed media. Not only does AoW have unrivaled art but also innovative utility. You will notice that each NFT has 3 skill traits on the bottom right of the image (Offense, Defense, and Resource). These scores will be very important and the alpha on them will be progressively revealed. Which faction will you join or will you collect all three?
